data.description: Great location near shopping, restaurants, freeway access, bus lines and very desirable schools! One level ranch on a large corner lot with a NEWER roof, vinyl windows, interior and exterior paint all done in 2015. Spacious kitchen offers granite counters, newer cabinets and newer hard wood floors. Refrigerator, washer and dryer all stay! Stay cozy in winters with the beautiful double sided floor to ceiling wood burning fireplace and stove and cool in summer with heat pump! This is a must see!
